# Remote Harness

Agentic task manager: Rust control plane, workers, CLI, and a web UI (scaffold under `web/`).

## Documentation

Specs and runbooks live in [`docs/`](docs/README.md). Start with [GETTING_STARTED.md](docs/GETTING_STARTED.md) (Docker Compose §1 or bare metal §2).

## Quick start (Docker)

From the repo root:

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

Postgres becomes healthy, then the **server** stub listens on [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) (`GET /health` → `ok`). Override the API key with `API_KEY` or a root `.env` file (see GETTING_STARTED §1.1).

## Rust workspace

```bash
cargo build --workspace
cargo run -p server
cargo run -p cli -- --version-marker
```

Crates: `crates/server`, `crates/worker`, `crates/cli`, `crates/api-types`.

## Web UI

The `web/` directory is a placeholder until the Vite + React app is added (plan task 22). See [TECH_STACK.md §7](docs/TECH_STACK.md#7-repo-layout-rust-monorepo).

